title: Ibiza: Secrets of the Party Island
overview: Ibiza: Secrets of the Party Island will explore how the glamorous party island operates over the course of one summer season.Zara first visited Ibiza in 2019 and fell in love with the Island. Having returned many times since as a holidaymaker, she now wants to discover how it all works from the inside. With unprecedented access and a rich cast of characters, Zara will seek to understand the Ibiza phenomenon and how the island is changing as it looks to attract a more upmarket clientele.
